{
  "stem": "321.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And England really accepted the refugees with open arms, to the great extent.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We became accepted like the British, in schools and in the evacuation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it has to be mentioned, I think, because I don't think it is known how decent the English were to the refugees.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And thousands of them went to England.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Zionists couldn't-- the Hakhsharot people couldn't go to Palestine, so England took her in-- took groups of these Zionist groups in with the Kindertransports.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So England was very generous.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I became British.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'm still British.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I felt had it not been, who knows?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That takes us to the war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my parents were bombed out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At one point, they had incendiary bombs and so on, so, you know, it wasn't all glorious.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was food rationing, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's amazing how little food you can do with, or what you can do without.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And with a Germanic upbringing, where you save everything anyway, that and a good combination, the rationing was pretty good.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It really was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then the war was finished, the VE.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I went to high school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I got my matriculation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we could not go to college straight from school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was still wartime, so you had to do wartime service, the high school graduates.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I wasn't sure-- I wanted to go into medicine at that time, but had to do some wartime work, and I went into a wartime day nursery and was put in with the real infants on the second floor-- and the doodlebugs.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The doodlebugs were unmanned bombs sent.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were not spotted by the radar.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you could-- there were V-1s and V-2s.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "V-1s had-- you had no chance.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
